  "texts": [
    "The comparative analysis between GA and RL has provided an understanding of each approach's efficacy in WCET estimation.",
    "RL's adaptability and learning-based exploration emerged as particularly advantageous in dynamically complex environments, consistently uncovering worst-case scenarios with greater precision than GA.",
    "This distinction underscores RL's potential as a preferred tool in applications where the stakes of accurate WCET estimation are high.Conversely, the exploration into GA revealed that incorporating diversity alongside execution time as composite fitness functions improves its capability.",
    "This enhancement allows for a broader exploration of the solution space, mitigates the risk of premature convergence, and diversifies exploration paths.",
    "Consequently, it improves the algorithm's overall performance."
  ],
